  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
    DEFINE INPUT PARAMETER iphMode AS HANDLE NO-UNDO.

    DEFINE VARIABLE lContinue AS LOGICAL   NO-UNDO.
    DEFINE VARIABLE rRowID    AS ROWID     NO-UNDO.
    
